  name: "Snowcaster"
  label: null
  type: null
  description: "At 9th level, an arctic druid can see normally in ice storm, sleet\
    \ storm, or similar natural snowstorms. In addition, she can prepare any druid\
    \ spell with the fire subtype1 as a cold spell, with an identical effect but inflicting\
    \ cold damage instead of fire damage.\nThis ability replaces venom immunity."
